arStrings.szText: "What is this place? Who are you?"
Primus, the communing pillar is quiet. I don’t know what has happened. We slaughtered the slaves like you said, but still the Three are silent. What have the faithful done to displease them?
Concerned. Speaking to someone in authority
No! Don’t go near it! We can no longer control – (pained screams)
Alarm. Shouts out to someone in the distance, then is cut off and attacked.
